Catalyst::Plugin::Alarm
================

Implements alarms with Time::HiRes for Catalyst.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Sys::SigAction (optional)
  Time::HiRes

